Class ExceptionToOrderedMapConvertor

java.lang.Object
  org.openadaptor.core.Component

          org.openadaptor.auxil.convertor.exception.ExceptionToOrderedMapConvertor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Administrable, IComponent, IDataProcessor
public class ExceptionToOrderedMapConvertor
extends AbstractConvertor

Converts a MessageException to an ordered map. This is to allow for further custom processing of exceptions, such as persisting them in a database.

Author:
Kris Lachor
